NeedsReviewCard is a CardView
    hide labels
    main column
        ReportSecurity.Role
            bold
            raise red alert when (NeedsReview)
                mouse over text is "ThisPolicyIsBeingUsedAndIsBasedOnADeliveredPolicyThatHasChangesNotReviewed"
            raise yellow alert when (not Status.Active)
                mouse over text is "ThisPolicyIsNotActive"
